citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:05
am-11:35 am on 10/30/2015.
I knocked on door and honked horn with no response. I called the home phone number, but got no answer.
